      <guid>https://sconti.tole.es/b0c8z95cjc-it-super-mario-rpg-videogioco-nintendo-ed.-italiana-.../</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;SUPER MARIO RPG-Videogioco Nintendo - Ed. Italiana - Versione su scheda&lt;/a&gt; qui:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/51FswAcs56L._SL500_._SL400_.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;SUPER MARIO RPG-Videogioco Nintendo - Ed. Italiana - Versione su scheda&#34;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;ℹ️:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Scopri uninattesa alleanza tra Mario, Bowser, Peach e due personaggi originali…Mallow e Geno!&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Corri incontro ai mostri per dare il via a un combattimento a turni con i tuoi tre personaggi. Premi il pulsante al momento giusto per unappagante dose di danni extra o per respingere un attacco.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Unisci le forze con uno strambo assortimento di eroi per salvare la Via Stellare e fermare la malvagia Banda di Fabbro Magno.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Il gioco offre una grafica completamente rinnovata e interamente 3D. Oltre alla grafica di gioco che vanta uno stile unico a livello visivo, inoltre tutti i filmati sono stati aggiornati e rimodernati&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🛒 Acquista qui!!&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;div&gt;&#xA;   Check the price of this item in other countries:&lt;p&gt;&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.co.uk/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees0a-21&#34;&gt;🇬🇧 United Kingdom&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees-20&#34;&gt;🇺🇸 USA&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.de/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees0ca-21&#34;&gt;🇩🇪 Germany&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.es/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees-21&#34;&gt;🇪🇸 Spain&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.fr/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees0d-21&#34;&gt;🇫🇷 France&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.it/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=tolees00-21&#34;&gt;🇮🇹 Italia&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.ae/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=rdkn01-21&#34;&gt;🇦🇪 Arab Emirates&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.ca/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=rdkn0d-20&#34;&gt;🇨🇦 Canada&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.com.be/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=rdkn0c-21&#34;&gt;🇧🇪 Belgium&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.nl/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=lgtm05-21&#34;&gt;🇳🇱 Neederlands&lt;/a&gt; |      &#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.pl/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=rdkn073-21&#34;&gt;🇵🇱 Poland&lt;/a&gt; |&#xA;      &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.amazon.se/dp/B0C8Z95CJC/?tag=rdkn0a-21&#34;&gt;🇸🇪 Sweden&lt;/a &gt; |&#xA;   &lt;/p&gt;</description>
